  <Subject Subject_ID="300025252">
    <Parent_Relationships>
      <Preferred_Parent>
        <Parent_Subject_ID>300025207</Parent_Subject_ID>
        <Relationship_Type>Parent/Child</Relationship_Type>
        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>people in commerce and business [300025207], people by occupation [300024980], people (agents) [300024979], People (hierarchy name) [300024978], Agents Facet [300264089]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
      </Preferred_Parent>
    </Parent_Relationships>
    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Generally, those employed in the business of making a consumer product directly or indirectly available to consumers; includes everyone in the chain of production and distribution, such as the manufacturers, wholesalers, distributers, and retailers.  Specifically in the construction business, those who provide materials, equipment, and prefabricated parts to contractors, subcontractors, or owners, but who usually do not do any installation or labor.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000044930/Black's Law Dictionary (1990)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000038891/Stein, Construction Glossary (1993)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Generalmente, aquellos que trabajan en el negocio de hacer productos de consumo directa o indirectamente dirigidos a los consumidores; incluidos todos aquellos que trabajan en la producción y distribución, tal como los fabricantes, distribuidores y minoristas. Específicamente en el área del negocio de la construcción, aquellos que proveen de materiales, equipos, y piezas prefabricadas a los contratistas, subcontratistas, o a ellos mismos, pero usualmente no realizan labores de instalación.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>In algemene zin, diegenen die zich bezighouden met het direct of indirect beschikbaar maken van consumentenproducten aan consumenten; omvat iedereen in de keten van productie en distributie, zoals fabrikanten, groothandelaars, distributeurs en detailhandelaars. In het bijzonder in de bouw: diegenen die materiaal, apparatuur en halffabricaten leveren aan aannemers, onderaannemers of eigenaren, maar die gewoonlijk geen installatiewerkzaamheden verrichten of arbeid leveren.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>泛指製造業的工作人員，生產之產品可能直接或間接供消費者使用；亦包含所有產銷供應鍊相關人員，如製造商、批發商、經銷商及零售商。可特指營造業中提供建材、設備及預製構件給承包商、分包商或業主者，通常不負責安裝或施工。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079740/AS-Academia Sinica data (2014-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
